	<h1 class="title">如何将美国总统打造成社交网络红人？这里有一组来自白宫的答案</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3121/small/3121.jpg?1440471388" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name"> Steven Levy </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-04-02 14:50:46 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/7968/medium/7968.jpg?1436695279" alt="" />			
	</div>
